        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/31511959/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/31511959/" class="">第280页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/3652404/" class=" " title="jakdan">jakdan</a>
                (澡雪精神)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="31511959">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">好的归汉族，次的归少数民族；汉族永远先进，少数民族总是愚昧。这是民族矛盾恶化的思想根源。 </span>
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/31511959/">(<span class="">3回应</span>)</a>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2014-05-07 12:14</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>好的归汉族，次的归少数民族；汉族永远先进，少数民族总是愚昧。这是民族矛盾恶化的思想根源。 </q></blockquote>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
